data.description: Why wait for the builder to finish your dream home when you can have this gem in the north side  of the Cape ready to be yours with only 2 years of use and new floor installed just 2 months ago. This gem shows a beautiful open floor plan with split bedroom and well distributed spaces ,just a block away from Kismet. This property is tenants occupied ,but they are excellent tenants and take care of the property if you want to keep then rented after the sale, they are currently in month to month lease. The property is not situated in a flood zone.
